# Prototype module scratch — a real engagement's /prototype/ is throwaway and
# regenerated on demand (never hand-edited, history ignored). This root-level
# rule does NOT match examples/sample-engagement/prototype/, which is committed
# as the golden fixture for the fm-prototype test.
/prototype/
